  • constructor

    Example

    const apiClient = new Zodios("https://jsonplaceholder.typicode.com", [
        {
          method: "get",
          path: "/users",
          description: "Get all users",
          parameters: [
            {
              name: "q",
              type: "Query",
              schema: z.string(),
            },
            {
              name: "page",
              type: "Query",
              schema: z.string().optional(),
            },
          ],
          response: z.array(z.object({ id: z.number(), name: z.string() })),
        }
      ]);
